skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: birthstone guide
des:
Know which birthstone corresponds to you and to the 12 months of the year.

Moreover with BIRTHSTONE PREMIUM, at very low cost, you'll know super interesting facts and more information about your birthstone like worldwide locations where it's found, healing properties attributed, uses and characteristics: color, types and shapes of crystals and so on.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
